    "SA also aids infectious disease surveillance (23) by tracking symptom mentions online (22) and measuring public awareness during outbreaks.",
    "Another significant area is monitoring population mental health, analyzing expressions of mood (7, 21, 34, 45, 53, 78) and sometimes attempting to identify suicide risk (44).",
